      <title>债券市场停止疯狂上涨，买家抢占 4.5% 收益率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/bond-market-halts-brutal-run-as-buyers-pounce-on-4-5-yields</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国债券市场在经历两个月的抛售后终于出现企稳迹象，每当收益率测试新高时，投资者就会开始纷纷入市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/bond-market-halts-brutal-run-as-buyers-pounce-on-4-5-yields</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Nov 2024 18:27:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>智利央行行长称特朗普将加剧贸易紧张局势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/trump-will-heighten-trade-tensions-chile-central-bank-head-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《第三报》援引采访报道，智利央行行长罗莎娜·科斯塔表示，她预计随着唐纳德·特朗普再次出任美国总统，贸易紧张局势将加剧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/trump-will-heighten-trade-tensions-chile-central-bank-head-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Nov 2024 18:08:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普胜利迫使华尔街一度发声的角落重组</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/trump-victory-forces-once-vocal-corner-of-wall-street-to-regroup</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫正迫使华尔街那些充满行话的圈子重新思考其谈话要点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/trump-victory-forces-once-vocal-corner-of-wall-street-to-regroup</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Nov 2024 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
