    <item>
      <title>罕见的阿尔及利亚 IPO 或将在 2025 年进行至少三笔交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/rare-algerian-ipo-may-be-followed-by-at-least-three-more-in-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿尔及利亚今年 3 月进行了 8 年来首次公开募股 (IPO)，预计 2025 年还将进行至少三次公开募股，以扩大其规模小且流动性差的股票交易所并实现经济多元化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/rare-algerian-ipo-may-be-followed-by-at-least-three-more-in-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Nov 2024 14:22:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国机构对阿达尼斯里兰卡项目进行尽职调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/us-agency-conducting-due-diligence-on-adani-s-sri-lanka-project</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家同意向阿达尼集团支持的斯里兰卡港口开发项目提供超过 5 亿美元贷款的美国机构表示，在该集团的亿万富翁创始人和其他高管受到贿赂指控后，它仍在对该项目进行尽职调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/us-agency-conducting-due-diligence-on-adani-s-sri-lanka-project</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Nov 2024 13:45:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新兴市场迎接“特朗普经济学” 垃圾债券面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/junk-bonds-at-risk-as-emerging-markets-brace-for-trumponomics</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 真的履行自己的承诺，新兴市场垃圾债上涨有可能只是过去四年债务危机与未来四年新一轮危机之间的一个插曲。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/junk-bonds-at-risk-as-emerging-markets-brace-for-trumponomics</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Nov 2024 13:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
